      each concept explained with intuition, math, and connections to the bigger picture.
    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-3">
      <a
        href="/modules/foundational-architecture"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-forest-700 px-6 py-3 text-[15px] font-medium text-cream-100 transition-all hover:bg-forest-600 hover:shadow-md no-underline"
      >
        Start with Module 01
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
        </svg>
      </a>
      <a
        href="/modules"
        class="inline-flex items-center rounded-lg border border-cream-300 px-6 py-3 text-[15px] font-medium text-forest-700 transition-all hover:bg-cream-50 hover:border-cream-300/80 no-underline"
      >
        Browse all modules
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
